# ASDD protected-path human gate (STANDARD §2.2).
#
# Every path here requires a review from a named human owner before merge, regardless of any agent
# verdict. Turn on branch protection for your default branch with "Require review from Code Owners"
# so this is enforced mechanically, not by convention. Keep this in sync with protected_paths in
# .asdd.yml.
#
# @welsbach is the interim sole maintainer. To let the maintainer set grow, create an org team
# (e.g. @OneHillAI/maintainers), add the members, and replace @welsbach here with the team.

# Default owner for everything.
*                       @welsbach

# Highest-risk: the standard, the security workflows, the PDP, and governance.
/STANDARD.md            @welsbach
/GOVERNANCE.md          @welsbach
/SECURITY.md            @welsbach
/.github/               @welsbach
/scripts/               @welsbach
/standards/             @welsbach
/.asdd.yml       @welsbach
